extendedInfo.description: Radio Libertad (Liberty Radio) are Spanish Christian radio stations. The format of this station is a variety of Spanish Christian music from Conjunto, Tejano, Mariachi, Salsa, Reggaton, Rock, Pop and Rap along with Praise & Worship.Radio Libertad provides the listener a taste of Spanish Christian music from all over the world. Artists include Marcos Witt, Jesus Adrian Romero, Lilly Goodman, Funky, Ericson Alexander Molano, Juan Carlos Alvarado, Samuel Hernandez, Marco Barrientos, and many more.Radio Libertad programs Spanish Christian music along with daily prayer programs in Corpus Christi and in the surrounding South Texas market. The unique styles of music and prayer are blended together to make an outstanding format that thousands of listeners, various churches and many businesses are enjoying.This app plays the live stream of Radio Libertad.Features:Volume controlBackground playbackStream stops automatically on incoming calls
